{"lemma":"مَشُورَةُ","slug":"مَشُورَةُ","root":"ش.#.ر","root_slug":"ش-_-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ش-_-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n23298","n23299"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8E%D8%B4%D9%8F%D9%88%D8%B1%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"counsel, recommendation, suggestion, consultation, advice"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ma.ʃuː.ra/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n23298","headword_ar":"مَشُورَةٌ","root":"$wr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see the next paragraph, in four places."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n23299","headword_ar":"مَشْوَرَةٌ","root":"$wr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ma$uwrapN","text_ar":"مَشُورَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uwraY","text_ar":"شُورَى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signify the same: (S:) the first and second are substs. from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aAwarahu","text_ar":"شَاوَرَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and the third is a subst. from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ta$aAwaruwA","text_ar":"تَشَاوَرُوا"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb:) or the first (Lth) and second [which is written in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ma$owarapN","text_ar":"مَشْوَرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (Lth, K) and third (K) are from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA_i$aArapu","text_ar":"الاـِشَارَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a$aAra Ealayohi","text_ar":"اَشَارَ عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) [they signify"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Consultation;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mutual debate in order that one may see another's opinion;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"counsel,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"advice:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a command, an order,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an injunction:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or] the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"extracting,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"drawing forth, opinion:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd, as mentioned above: see 6:) ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ma$uwrapN","text_ar":"مَشُورَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ma$owarapN","text_ar":"مَشْوَرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"] is of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mafoEulapN","text_ar":"مَفْعُلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [originally"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ma$owurapN","text_ar":"مَشْوُرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mafoEalapN","text_ar":"مَفْعَلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] not"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mafoEuwlapN","text_ar":"مَفْعُولَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,) because it is an inf. n., [or rather a quasi-inf. n.,] and such a noun has not this last measure: (TA:) it is like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maEuwnapN","text_ar":"مَعُونَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Msb;) and is a contraction of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ma$owurapN","text_ar":"مَشْوُرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Fr, TA:) and it is said also to be from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aAra Ald~aAb~apa","text_ar":"شَارَ الدَّابَّةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; or, accord. to some, from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aAra AlEasala","text_ar":"شَارَ العَسَلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; good counsel or advice being likened to honey. (Msb.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealayoka biA@loma$owarapi fiY A^umuwrika","text_ar":"عَلَيْكَ بِا@لْمَشْوَرَةِ فِى اُمُورِكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biA@loma$uwrapi","text_ar":"بِا@لْمَشُورَةِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Keep thou to consultation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"take counsel, in thine affairs"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN jay~idu Alma$uwrapi","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ جَيِّدُ المَشُورَةِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alma$owarapi","text_ar":"المَشْوَرَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one is good,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"excellent, in consultation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"counsel"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^amoruhumo $uwraY","text_ar":"اَمْرُهُمْ شُورَى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bayonahumo","text_ar":"بَيْنَهُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Amrhm fawoDaY bynhm","text_ar":"امرهم فَوْضَى بينهم"},{"kind":"text","text":", ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Their affair,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"case, is a thing to be determined by consultation among themselves,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] i. e., none of them is to appropriate a thing to himself exclusively of others. (Msb.) It is said of 'Omar, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taraka AlxilaAfapa $uwraY","text_ar":"تَرَكَ الخِلَافَةَ شُورَى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, Mgh)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He left the office of Khaleefeh as a thing to be determined by consultation:"},{"kind":"text","text":"for he assigned it to one of six; not particularizing for it any one of them; namely, 'Othmán and 'Alee and Talhah and Ez-Zubeyr and 'Abd-Er-Rahmán Ibn-'Owf and Saad Ibn-Abee-Wakkás. (Mgh.) And one says also, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~aAsu fiyhi $uwraY","text_ar":"النَّاسُ فِيهِ شُورَى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The people are to determine by consultation respecting it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","Lth","K","TA","Fr","A","Mgh"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}